com.github.mlaursen.database.objects

Class MyResultSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.mlaursen.database.objects.MyResultSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<MyResultRow>

    public class MyResultSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<MyResultRow>
    A version of a SQL ResultSet. The only difference is that this is a List of MyResultRows instead of a ResultSet that must be closed.
    Author:
    mlaursen
